{"tid":1334272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"京都動畫遭縱火33人死 41歲犯人被捕後小聲怒斥京都動畫「抄襲」","createTime":"2019-07-20T04:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T06:10:51.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"209961e74a7a5af4c699482c8f9e96defddf28bf","tid":1334272,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://asahichinese-f.com/society/12554290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasahichinese-f.com%2Fsociety%2F12554290&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=b2e75f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asahichinese-f.com/society/12554290</a><br />\n<br />\n  猛烈的火焰及黑煙於18日早上，瞬間吞噬了京都市伏見區「京都動畫(Kyoto Animation)」第1製作所的3層樓建築。雖然附近的居民等人也拚命地進行救援，但仍釀成已確認33人死亡的慘烈事故。<br />\n<br />\n  根據京都府警表示，公司內外部的員工等共74人所在的大樓中，於上午10點半左右遭男子從1樓的入口闖入。<br />\n<br />\n  「去死！」<br />\n<br />\n  男子將手中如汽油般的液體灑在１樓並點火，火焰伴隨著「咚」的爆炸聲竄出，周圍也被黑煙包圍。當時正在附近工作的22歲男性表示：「聽到2、3次爆炸聲。火焰轉眼間就擴散開來，一直到3樓為止的所有窗戶都有火舌竄出。」<br />\n<br />\n  點火後男子隨即逃至大樓外，通過住宅區內的小路，朝向距離該地以南約100公尺處的京阪電鐵宇治線六地藏站前進。<br />\n<br />\n  上午10點35分過後，住在附近的61歲女性一從自家出門，便看見在玄關附近有名仰躺著的男子。其身穿T恤及牛仔褲，右腳還冒出了小火苗及煙霧，且當時是處於沒有穿鞋、腳上沾有血跡的狀態。該男子身形壯碩魁梧，頭髮則有燒焦。據了解，他的呼吸斷斷續續，女性雖向其詢問「還好嗎？」，然而並沒有獲得回答。<br />\n<br />\n  根據府警表示，一路緊追的製作所男性員工隨後壓制住該名男子，並於上午10點41分將其交給趕到的伏見署員。根據女性表示，署員向男子詢問「為什麼要做這種事？」、「從哪裡進入建築物的？」等。而男子像是對什麼感到憤怒的模樣，用小聲而清楚的語調說了「誰叫他們抄襲！」、「放了火」等。 <br />\n<br />\n  據府警表示，從男子的駕照上得知其現年41歲且居住在埼玉市，他在當下曾說明「在1樓灑下液體後放了火」。而由於男子的手、腳、胸部及臉部等被燒傷，已送往京都市內的醫院。"},{"pid":"69c5e7368ae7db362440534c33d96ebfbea129f9","tid":1334272,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7279d2b057f67d7d3b9209ed9cf45c4dbdd73afe","tid":1334272,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"如果林奠高官同狗屋企人嘅資料用marker 寫係公廁廁格 會點？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dmcjFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dmcjFS</a>"},{"pid":"8c4ce5a2fb0188f6dd285a84d90dfab59dd22b4d","tid":1334272,"uid":30163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"38dd7b19c05453e5ba029fed864a35095b392edc","tid":1334272,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5753d6ee069edac00e43ebcf727ab90a9f762a","tid":1334272,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75df0940485b8bebf17a0ea8050704afb674ae4e","tid":1334272,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4ce5a2fb0188f6dd285a84d90dfab59dd22b4d","tid":1334272,"uid":30163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41aeacce03dc3e414ab370cd6f07ccc9b81a5e9","tid":1334272,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"抄你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946adc2d3fa4414f1096b5367e25d13275900cfd","tid":1334272,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死返動物台講飽佢啦,講左三日又貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}